span.p:
Workflow:
1. Edit database.yaml add column
2. Run generate_schema.py
3. SchemaInfo.h updated with new constant
4a. Use constant in repository code Manual Qt SQL
4b. OR use constant in ORM mapping QxOrm
5. Create migration SQL file
6. Run migrate.py to apply
7. Commit YAML + generated files together

• QxOrm registration uses Schema constants
• Schema changes cause compile errors if ORM outdated
• Single source of truth: database.yaml
• No duplication of table/column names
